    "From the table, we see that (1) FedAvg [20] consistently outperforms local training, demonstrating the effectiveness of FL for LLMs in the medical domain.",
    "(2) Though no FL algorithm can consistently achieve the best on every metric, FedAdam [54] achieves the best on 4 out of 9 metrics, making it a relatively better algorithm for this scenario.",
    "Federated Instruction Tuning on Code DatasetsExperimental setups.",
    "We use a code generation dataset, CodeAlpacafoot_5, as the training dataset [69].During training, we set the client number as 10, where we randomly sample 2 clients to be available for each round.",
    "These clients hold 20k data samples in total."
